Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who are bound by a contract may enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have awakened to your power most brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the Contractor's Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From this night forth, you are our guest in the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Persona ability is that of the wild card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that of others, it is very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is like the number zero: Empty, yet holding infinite potential within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to traveling the road of your destiny together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}to see where your awakened power of the wild card will take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Satonaka! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd the monsters go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was seriously amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you call it... "Persona," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just get out of here before more of those things come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,An exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First, tell me what happened to the Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean those monsters back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you provoke them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear-ish the thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it up to here with people barging in here and riling up the Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,TVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now off with you! Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a busy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!{I'm glad to be alive!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take advantage of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same poster I saw over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's Hiiragi Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been on the news a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband's the one who had the affair with the announcer that died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. What about that freaky room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be connected to the death of Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think my heart can take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit, I forgot! I gotta go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is giving me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel so good. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through hell yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you some other time, but you probably won't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're Yukiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for a while now, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out and have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You're scaring her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Amagi challenge ain't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, are you coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was obviously asking you out on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cruel, Amagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the same thing to me last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go out then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart already belongs to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, she hasn't texted me back since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She left after her family called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They needed her help at the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Her family owns the nicest traditional inn in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yukiko is the heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?{senpai=Konishi}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She still hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The principal has something to say, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking out of turn will earn you a spot on my shit list!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret to inform you that I have a terrible announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi Saki of Class 3-B was found dead early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been assured by the faculty that she wasn't the victim of bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body was hung like Ms. Yamano's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a telephone pole this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you guys watch the Midnight Channel last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna talk about that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was bothering me, so I watched it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I saw Konishi on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our classmates saw Ms. Yamano on the Midnight Channel and claimed she was his soul mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I heard that Konishi vanished before her death, just like Ms. Yamano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be a coincidence.{Could that :really: be a coincidence?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think people who show up on TV die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how we saw a poster of Hiiragi Misuzu over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the TV world is connected to the murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi and Ms. Yamano may have gone in there at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to come back once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go in from the same location, maybe we'll meet that bear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maybe" isn't good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could really use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka, I'm leaving you in charge of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This was never gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you two again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same place after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are bear-y suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I can tell someone's been throwing people in here before the fog lifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that if it's foggy on your side, the fog lifts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I do recall it being foggy on the days Ms. Yamano and Konishi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone forced you in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so you must be the one's throwing people in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that Konishi and Ms. Yamano were thrown into this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you guys did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How do we know {\i1}you{\i0} didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off that stupid costume and show us your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty! What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you bear-y much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, does {\i1}anything{\i0} faze you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll believe that you guys aren't the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to find the real guy who did all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to live here in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this thing for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only ones who can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're going along with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being way too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You better help us out then, stupid bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can see so clearly with these on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this looks like the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I last saw a girl over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you dumb bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the girl you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She disappeared into that store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her family's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish Junes would go under.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I heard that Konishi's daughter is working there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could she, with her family's business suffering like it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a troublesome child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saki, how many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the eldest daughter of the {Konishi }family who owns this liquor store, aren't you ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How dare you get a part-time job at Junes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her dad's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can we hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is someone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the ticket I gave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never had the chance to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always wanted to tell Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that he was a real pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was only nice to him because he was the store manager's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he takes it completely the wrong way and gets all enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain in the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who cares about Junes, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The liquor store, the shopping district, my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish everything would just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying! This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who thinks everything's a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, "me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two Yosukes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And coming here for Konishi's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a load of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You just came because you thought it sounded like a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What else is there to do out in this shithole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If all went well, hey, maybe you could even be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And your sweetheart's death was the perfect excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}your{\i0} Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck that! I don't know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. I'm me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not you anymore, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That Shadow's getting bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Hanamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You really hit it hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing came from you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You put on a good show of being carefree and happy-go-lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause you're so terrified of being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not me! I don't know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's attracting nearby Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, if we don't stop him soon, this'll get grizzly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how pathetic you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's ask Hanamura to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The prince of Junes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He thinks everyone depends on him because he's the manager's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew you were a nuisance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but you played the part of the good guy well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Booyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He takes it completely the wrong way and gets all enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked her out 'cause you're sick of living in the boonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to do something fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now disappear!{shadow yosuke}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You loved her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She dumped ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wasn't lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was so ashamed that I didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To get along with others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to change the way I acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I think I'm annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But my feelings for her were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's a part of me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get down to it, all of this is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Shut up, you brat!{if I hear one more uzzee I'm going to kill someone}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi!{TS sign: Burning up!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is my...{yos}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Persona.{yu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really saved my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The rope got cut off, and I had no idea what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerve of you guys! You're such morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this! You guys suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Satonaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me ten steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me ten steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we accept your terms for forgiveness, right, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, it'll be beef bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Konishi and Ms. Yamano were thrown into that dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(17,309,\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}The people who came in here were attacked by their Shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(3244,3787,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}just like Yosuke was a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone really did throw them in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find the culprit and stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} did, anyway.{You did, yeah.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that, with you, I can find the culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it true that you're the manager, even though you're still in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm only filling in for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're looking gorgeous in that kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it true that Ms. Yamano stayed at your inn before she died?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to do the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura! Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.69,0:24:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.73,0:24:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.82,0:24:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
